      <for each due: • <id> (applied, due <date>) → <target-basename>: <metric>>
      Record: /adapt outcome <id> <improved|no-change|regressed|inconclusive> [note]  ·  Scoreboard: /adapt score"
      Cap at 5 lines; if more, list 5 and say "…and the rest via /adapt due". Do NOT tag any outcome yourself — surfacing only; the verdict is Steve's (or a future eval agent's) call.

PASS 3 — LOG (always, exactly one short section):
